title: John Legend - (VEVO GO Shows) All Of Me  [FLAC]
description:
John Legend performed live in New York City in December of 2013 as part of VEVO GO Shows series. With just piano and voice he enchanted a throng of people at Manhattan's Standard Hotel. The patrons were uninformed that the show was going to take place, and their surprise is evident. The song is "All Of Me," from Legend's 2013 album 'Love In The Future.'
